# Environment Variables for Election Guide & Timeline Assistant

# ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# GOOGLE MAPS API KEY
# ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Used for: Embedded map in "Find My Polling Place"
# How to get one:
#   1. Go to https://console.cloud.google.com/
#   2. Create or select a project
#   3. APIs & Services → Library → enable "Maps Embed API"
#   4. APIs & Services → Credentials → Create API Key
#   5. Restrict the key to your domain for security
#
VITE_GOOGLE_MAPS_API_KEY=

# ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# GOOGLE OAUTH 2.0 CLIENT ID
# ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Used for: "Add to Calendar" Google Calendar integration
# How to get one:
#   1. Go to https://console.cloud.google.com/
#   2. APIs & Services → OAuth consent screen → External
#   3. APIs & Services → Credentials → Create OAuth 2.0 Client ID
#   4. Application type: Web Application
#   5. Authorized JavaScript origins: http://localhost:5173
#   6. Enable "Google Calendar API" in the Library
#
# NOTE: Without this key, "Add to Calendar" falls back to opening
#       a pre-filled Google Calendar link in a new tab (no auth needed).
#
VITE_GOOGLE_CLIENT_ID=
